            "title": "京東去季利潤跌56% 仍勝預期",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"京東去季利潤跌56% 仍勝預期\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jdQTCUOU_0CXq0c3hhV.5g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-10/4d91dc80-b391-11f0-bb7b-1fa034eab90a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">京東去季利潤跌56% 仍勝預期</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
